==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pioneers Day
<hw>Pi`o*neers'" Day</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>In Utah, a legal holiday,
July 24, commemorated the arrival, in 1847, of Brigham Young and his
followers at the present site of Salt Lake City.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pioner</ent>⟦br⟧
